Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: This Jedi was a female Togruta who served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic decades prior to the Great Galactic War. This Jedi trained Ngani Zho as well as two humans and a Zabrak at the ruins of the old Jedi Enclave on Dantooine.
Zho would remember his old master when reminiscing on his past later in 3643 BBY.
